<HEADLINE>
FT  23 JUL 92 / UK Company News: BWD Securities falls to Pounds 1.22m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BWD Securities, the USM-quoted financial services group, reported a 10 per
cent fall in pre-tax profits, from Pounds 1.36m to Pounds 1.22m, in the six
months to May 31.
Turnover rose to Pounds 5.7m (Pounds 5.2m) but administrative expenses
increased and operating profits declined to Pounds 903,000 (Pounds 1.03m).
Interest receivable was Pounds 320,000 (Pounds 333,000).
The interim dividend is maintained at 1.3p, payable from earnings of 4.5p
(5.2p).
</TEXT>
