(C4 at 10.50pm) holds out the promise of being every bit as cryptic, torrid,
and absurd as part one. I should warn you that the priapic hermit gets his
come-uppance in a particularly nasty fashion which may well be a first for
British TV.
Legendary Latin lover of all times, Casanova gave his name to the Complex
which will be discussed tonight in Men Talk (C4 at 10.20pm.)
